why?\n\nAs you descend through the levels of the bunker, you begin to work out what happened in this place and why you're here. In the end it becomes a race against time, with high stakes and difficult challenges.\n\nThis is an adventure-style game, all about exploration and problem-solving. There are no zombies, no \"jump scares\" and nothing is trying to kill you. It's just you against the bunker, as you try to find your way out.\nNote -- this is a small game, with an estimated play-through time of about half an hour.", "short_description": "This is a short adventure-style game, all about exploration and problem-solving. There are no zombies, no \"jump scares\" and nothing is trying to kill you. It's just you against the bunker, as you try to find your way out."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://www.tiriam.com/#%21bunker14%2Fcs7r3", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.tiriam.com/#%21bunker14%2Fcs7r3", "publisher_name": "Tiriam Immersive Media", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.tiriam.com/#%21bunker14%2Fcs7r3", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["EXPLORATION", "ADVENTURE", "PUZZLE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["TOUCHPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "323154106528627"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12449016_500595363474300_32568515_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ZmyN3kX7MEwQ7kNvgFln_9z&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD5n6G9cRQUqlnGBL1N1uBuyaD2TGFuxIN